      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON JOY (4) drifted back settling but did best work late to finish 5th at this track over 400m (23.22). Has claims if she runs up to expectations. FOOLS RUSH IN (8) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and four placings from nine starts. In the money last time at Maitland (22.75) in a Grade 5, finishing a 0.8 lengths second. Can hit the frame with the right run. BILLY BLINDERS (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 23.04 beating Kalani Sea. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Significant danger. SUBSONIC (1) warrants respect with the drop in journey.",
